description:
Multi-purpose beauty tool for quick, easy & pain-free removal of facial hair and dermaplaning.

Dual ended blade razors make it easy to dermaplane around the cheek area and allow for precision on intricate brows & lip area. High quality Japanese stainless steel with fine mesh protected blades for safety. Ideal for creating smooth, radiant skin instantly; resulting in a perfect canvas for flawless make up application. Also helps to improve skincare active absorption.

Dermaplaning tool.

Quick, easy and pain-free removal of facial hair.

Dual ended blade razors including precision blade.

Japanese stainless steel with fine micro-mesh technology for safety.

Create smooth, radiant skin instantly!
name: Manicare Dermasmooth Fuzz Remover 2pk
